&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CT Radiographer &lt;/strong&gt;– Hampshire Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PREVIOUS APPLICANTS NEED NOT APPLY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; Basingstoke and North Hampshire Hospital or Royal Hampshire County Hospital Winchester. &lt;strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;(If you have a preferred site, please indicate this in your supporting information on your application.)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for Radiographers with a commitment to outstanding patient care and high quality imaging to join our friendly and dynamic CT team at HHFT.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are currently expanding our service and have vacancies for Band 6 CT Radiographers to be based at either Royal Hampshire County Hospital (RHCH), Winchester or Basingstoke and North Hampshire Hospital (BNHH) .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience in CT Imaging is an advantage, but not essential, as full training will be provided.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Working Hours: 37.5 hours per week variable shifts including evenings, nights and weekends. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we look for:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;HCPC registered Radiographers with appropriate post graduate experience who align with our Trust’s core values&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactive individuals who are motivated and enthusiastic about CT imaging.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good communicators with an ability to work both autonomously and in a team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we offer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This is an exciting time to join HHFT as the Trust plans to implement a fully managed equipment replacement programme in 2020. This will result in department refurbishment and installation of new imaging equipment with the latest technology.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;HHFT supports specialist services for rare or complex conditions such as pseudomyxoma peritonei for patients across the UK and with the expansion of Radiology services this is an ideal opportunity to expand your portfolio in in CT imaging.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The Winchester site has two GE scanners: one HD Discovery and an Optima undertaking a variety of examinations site is a busy Stroke unit delivering high quality care which demands CT heads/CT Angiography within the hour in line with NICE Guidelines for Stroke.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The Basingstoke site has two Siemens scanners: one Flash and an AS with a shared control room, undertaking a variety of examinations including CT Colonography and Cardiac CT There may also be the opportunity to train/work in MRI in addition to CT.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Encouragement to engage in professional and service development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supportive friendly teams, both in Radiology and across the Trust&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who we are: &lt;/strong&gt;We are a busy Radiology Department who undertake examinations in many modalities, across 4 sites. The main facilities are at Royal Hampshire County Hospital (RHCH) and Basingstoke and North Hampshire Hospital (BNHH) with satellite services at Andover War Memorial Hospital and Alton Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the trust: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The vision at Hampshire Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust is to provide outstanding care for every patient. HHFT employs circa 6,000 people and serves a population of nearly 600,000 people across Hampshire and West Berkshire as well as some people who access our specialist services from across the country.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Trust prioritises the provision of exceptional, compassionate, care delivered by the valued staff working in a culture of collaboration and mutual respect.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Four core values (CARE) Compassion, Accountability, Respect and Encourage are in place to support provision of outstanding patient care, empowering all members of staff, sustainable growth and innovating for the future.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt; #AspiringToBeTheBest &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
